item.title: Home
item.dc:creator: demouser
item.content:encoded:
Michelle

Free Accessibility Ready
WordPress Theme

by WebManDesign.eu

Example home pages

Theme demo content provides selection of industry specific home page examples. Get inspired and adapt them to your needs and your use case.

Demo pages were built with included block patterns and simple basic blocks.
Besides home page examples you also get selection of pages such as "Contact", "Portfolio", "Services", "FAQ" and "About" page.

Theme features

Inclusive

Inclusivity and accessibility is built directly into this theme. Make internet a better place and build an accessible website now.

Block patterns & styles

Build your website easier and faster with native WordPress drag and drop block editor and predefined library of block patterns and styles.

Custom footer

No more widgets in the footer - now you have full creative control to build your website footer using block editor!

Templates

Want your pages and posts to have a different layout and display? Just choose one of predefined templates and enjoy.

Featured posts

Display selection of your posts as featured on your blog page. With hover animation, while still perfectly accessible.

Fast!

Let your website visitors experience fast loading pages! Be amazed with how speed optimized this theme is.

Get creative now!

Why hesitate? Grab this free theme now and get creative with it. You will love it!

Get Michelle Theme →
